/></p></div><div
class="type-defaults"><p><strong>When Is a Good Time to Act?</strong><br
/></p><p>Now! Every week brings new signs of speeding climate change, along with new ways to reduce its worst effects. Every commitment and innovation brings new hope. Likewise the urgency is clear on affordable housing and social equity.</p><p>But it won't be automatic. ESG needs to be a top-down mandate in every organization, not just an enthusiasm for a few. Hard choices will be necessary.</p><p>Our industry can be a hero in this story. Will we?</p></div></div><div
